# -------------------------------------------------------
# Credentials & Secrets — NEVER commit these
# Patterns to watch for:
#   - iam.panserviceaccount.com  → Palo Alto SASE service account
#   - client_secret / client_id  → OAuth / API keys
#   - *.pem / *.key              → TLS private keys
#   - .env*                      → local environment files
# -------------------------------------------------------
credentials.json
**/credentials.json
secrets.json
**/secrets.json
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx

